      <title>特朗普陪审团在 12 张图片中看到了哪些对他不利的证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/-pay-with-cash-the-evidence-against-trump-at-hush-money-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普历史性的封口费审判很快将由纽约陪审团审理，该陪审团必须决定这位前总统是否伪造了公司记录，以隐瞒向色情明星斯托米·丹尼尔斯支付的封口费并影响 2016 年大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/-pay-with-cash-the-evidence-against-trump-at-hush-money-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
